<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none"><font color="rgb(34, 34, 34)" face="sans-serif" size="14px">An</font></span><font color="rgb(34, 34, 34)" face="sans-serif" size="14px"><span>&#160;</span><b style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">energy tax</b><span>&#160;</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none">is a</span><span>&#160;</span></font><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tax" title="Tax" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-color: rgb(255,; background-position: 255, 255); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)" face="sans-serif" size="14px">tax</font></a><span><font color="rgb(34, 34, 34)" face="sans-serif" size="14px">&#160;</font></span><font color="rgb(34, 34, 34)" face="sans-serif" size="14px"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none">that increases the price of</span><span>&#160;</span></font><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Energy" title="Energy" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-color: rgb(255,; background-position: 255, 255); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)" face="sans-serif" size="14px">energy</font></a><span><font color="rgb(34, 34, 34)" face="sans-serif" size="14px">&#160;</font></span><font color="rgb(34, 34, 34)" face="sans-serif" size="14px"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none">(Fisher</span><span>&#160;</span><i style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">et al</i><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none">., 1996, p.&#160;416).</span></font><font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)" face="sans-serif"><sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Energy_tax#cite_note-1" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[1]</a></sup></font><span><font color="rgb(34, 34, 34)" face="sans-serif" size="14px">&#160;</font></span><font color="rgb(34, 34, 34)" face="sans-serif" size="14px"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none">Arguments in favour of energy taxes have included the pursuit of</span><span>&#160;</span></font><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Macroeconomic" class="mw-redirect" title="Macroeconomic" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-color: rgb(255,; background-position: 255, 255); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)" face="sans-serif" size="14px">macroeconomic</font></a><span><font color="rgb(34, 34, 34)" face="sans-serif" size="14px">&#160;</font></span><font color="rgb(34, 34, 34)" face="sans-serif" size="14px"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none">objectives, e.g.,</span><span>&#160;</span></font><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fiscal_deficit" class="mw-redirect" title="Fiscal deficit" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-color: rgb(255,; background-position: 255, 255); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)" face="sans-serif" size="14px">fiscal deficit</font></a><span><font color="rgb(34, 34, 34)" face="sans-serif" size="14px">&#160;</font></span><font color="rgb(34, 34, 34)" face="sans-serif" size="14px"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none">reduction in the 1990s, as well as environmental benefits, i.e., reduced pollution (Nellor, 1994, p.&#160;1).</span></font><font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)" face="sans-serif"><sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Energy_tax#cite_note-2" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[2]</a></sup></font><span><font color="rgb(34, 34, 34)" face="sans-serif" size="14px">&#160;</font></span><font color="rgb(34, 34, 34)" face="sans-serif" size="14px"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none">A weakness of energy taxes is that they impose a burden (or cost) in the form of reduced economic output and employment (p.&#160;19)</span></font>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
