      <span class="mw-headline" id="CO2_and_global_warming">CO<font size="13.44px"><sub style="line-height: 1; font-size: 13.44px">2</sub></font></span><span>&#160;</span><span class="mw-headline" id="CO2_and_global_warming">and global warming</span><span class="mw-editsection-bracket" style="margin-right: 0; color: rgb(84, 89, 93)"><font color="rgb(84, 89, 93)" size="small" face="sans-serif">[</font></span><span class="mw-editsection" style="font-size: small; font-weight: normal; margin-left: 0; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; font-family: sans-serif; white-space: nowrap"><font size="small" face="sans-serif" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Carbon_tax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: CO2 and global warming" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">edit</a></font></span><span class="mw-editsection-bracket" style="margin-left: 0; color: rgb(84, 89, 93)"><font color="rgb(84, 89, 93)" size="small" face="sans-serif">]</font></span>
