      Main article:<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_pricing_in_Australia" title="Carbon pricing in Australia" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">Carbon pricing in Australia</font></a>
