<node ID="ID_1793313452" CREATED="1553798487056" MODIFIED="1553798487056" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fifth_Labour_Government"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
      In 2005, the<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fifth_Labour_Government" class="mw-redirect" title="Fifth Labour Government" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">Fifth Labour Government</font></a><span>&#160;</span>proposed a carbon tax in order to meet obligations under the<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kyoto_Protocol" title="Kyoto Protocol" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">Kyoto Protocol</font></a>. The proposal would have set an emissions price of NZ$15 per tonne of CO<font size="11.2px"><sub style="line-height: 1; font-size: 11.2px">2</sub></font>-equivalent. The planned tax was scheduled to take effect from April 2007, and applied across most economic sectors though with an exemption for<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Methane" title="Methane" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">methane</font></a><span>&#160;</span>emissions from farming and provisions for special exemptions from carbon intensive businesses if they adopted world's-best-practice standards of emissions.<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-88" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-88" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[88]</a></sup></font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node ID="ID_65474998" CREATED="1553798487059" MODIFIED="1553798487059" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_Zealand_general_election,_2005"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
      After the<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_Zealand_general_election,_2005" class="mw-redirect" title="New Zealand general election, 2005" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">2005 election</font></a>, some of the minor parties supporting the<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fifth_Labour_Government" class="mw-redirect" title="Fifth Labour Government" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">Fifth Labour Government</font></a><span>&#160;</span>(<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NZ_First" class="mw-redirect" title="NZ First" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">NZ First</font></a><span>&#160;</span>and<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_Future" title="United Future" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">United Future</font></a>) opposed the proposed tax, and it was abandoned in December 2005.<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-89" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-89" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[89]</a></sup></font><span>&#160;</span>In 2008, the<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_Zealand_Emissions_Trading_Scheme" title="New Zealand Emissions Trading Scheme" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">New Zealand Emissions Trading Scheme</font></a><span>&#160;</span>was enacted via the<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Climate_Change_Response_(Emissions_Trading)_Amendment_Act_2008" title="Climate Change Response (Emissions Trading) Amendment Act 2008" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">Climate Change Response (Emissions Trading) Amendment Act 2008</font></a>.<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-90" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-90" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[90]</a></sup></font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
</node>
<node FOLDED="true" ID="ID_266845992" CREATED="1553798487060" MODIFIED="1553798487060" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Carbon_tax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=23"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <h3 style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255,; background-position: 255, 255); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.6; font-family: sans-serif; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px">
      <span class="mw-headline" id="Europe">Europe</span><span class="mw-editsection-bracket" style="margin-right: 0; color: rgb(84, 89, 93)"><font color="rgb(84, 89, 93)" size="small" face="sans-serif">[</font></span><span class="mw-editsection" style="font-size: small; font-weight: normal; margin-left: 0; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; font-family: sans-serif; white-space: nowrap"><font size="small" face="sans-serif" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Carbon_tax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=23" title="Edit section: Europe" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">edit</a></font></span><span class="mw-editsection-bracket" style="margin-left: 0; color: rgb(84, 89, 93)"><font color="rgb(84, 89, 93)" size="small" face="sans-serif">]</font></span>
    </h3>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<node ID="ID_1927016419" CREATED="1553798487062" MODIFIED="1553798487062" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-bashmakov-24"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
      In Europe, a number of countries have imposed energy taxes or energy taxes based partly on carbon content.<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-bashmakov_24-3" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-bashmakov-24" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[24]</a></sup></font><span>&#160;</span>These include Denmark, Finland, Germany, Ireland, Italy, the Netherlands, Norway, Slovenia, Sweden, Switzerland, and the UK. None of these countries has been able to introduce a uniform carbon tax for fuels in all sectors. For a review of Europe's experience with carbon taxation see Andersen (2010).<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-91" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-91" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[91]</a></sup></font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1197500761" CREATED="1553798487064" MODIFIED="1553798487064" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Carbon_tax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=24"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <h4 style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255,; background-position: 255, 255); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: sans-serif; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px">
      <span class="mw-headline" id="European_Union">European Union</span><span class="mw-editsection-bracket" style="margin-right: 0; color: rgb(84, 89, 93)"><font color="rgb(84, 89, 93)" size="small" face="sans-serif">[</font></span><span class="mw-editsection" style="font-size: small; font-weight: normal; margin-left: 0; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; font-family: sans-serif; white-space: nowrap"><font size="small" face="sans-serif" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Carbon_tax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=24" title="Edit section: European Union" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">edit</a></font></span><span class="mw-editsection-bracket" style="margin-left: 0; color: rgb(84, 89, 93)"><font color="rgb(84, 89, 93)" size="small" face="sans-serif">]</font></span>
    </h4>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<node ID="ID_76034751" CREATED="1553798487067" MODIFIED="1553798487067" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/European_Union"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
      During the 1990s, a carbon/energy tax was proposed at the<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/European_Union" title="European Union" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">EU</font></a><span>&#160;</span>level but failed due to industrial lobbying.<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-pearce_92-0" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-pearce-92" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[92]</a></sup></font><span>&#160;</span>In 2010, the European Commission considered implementing a pan-European minimum tax on pollution permits purchased under the<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/European_Union_Greenhouse_Gas_Emissions_Trading_Scheme" class="mw-redirect" title="European Union Greenhouse Gas Emissions Trading Scheme" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">European Union Greenhouse Gas Emissions Trading Scheme</font></a><span>&#160;</span>(EU ETS) in which the proposed new tax would be calculated in terms of carbon content rather than volume, so that fuels with high energy concentrations, despite their subsequently high carbon content, will no longer carry the same traditionally low price.<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-93" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-93" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[93]</a></sup></font>According to the European Commission, the new plan will charge firms a minimum tax per tonne of carbon dioxide emissions<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-94" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-94" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[94]</a></sup></font><span>&#160;</span>at a suggested rate of &#8364;4 to &#8364;30 per tonne of CO<font size="11.2px"><sub style="line-height: 1; font-size: 11.2px">2</sub></font>.<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-95" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-95" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[95]</a></sup></font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node FOLDED="true" ID="ID_403501894" CREATED="1553798487070" MODIFIED="1553798487070" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Carbon_tax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=25"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <h4 style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255,; background-position: 255, 255); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0px; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: sans-serif; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px">
      <span class="mw-headline" id="Denmark">Denmark</span><span class="mw-editsection-bracket" style="margin-right: 0; color: rgb(84, 89, 93)"><font color="rgb(84, 89, 93)" size="small" face="sans-serif">[</font></span><span class="mw-editsection" style="font-size: small; font-weight: normal; margin-left: 0; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; font-family: sans-serif; white-space: nowrap"><font size="small" face="sans-serif" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Carbon_tax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=25" title="Edit section: Denmark" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">edit</a></font></span><span class="mw-editsection-bracket" style="margin-left: 0; color: rgb(84, 89, 93)"><font color="rgb(84, 89, 93)" size="small" face="sans-serif">]</font></span>
    </h4>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<node ID="ID_1704786852" CREATED="1553798487073" MODIFIED="1553798487073" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Danish_krone"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
      As of the year 2002, the standard carbon tax rate since 1996 amounts to 100<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Danish_krone" title="Danish krone" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">DKK</font></a><span>&#160;</span>per tonne of CO<font size="11.2px"><sub style="line-height: 1; font-size: 11.2px">2</sub></font>, equivalent to approximately &#8364;13 or US$18. Net carbon emission tax from fuel combustion can vary depending on the level of pollution each source emits, the tax rate varies between 402 DKK per tonne of oil to 5.6 DKK per tonne of natural gas and 0 for non-combustible renewables. The rate for electricity is 1164 DKK per tonne or 10 &#248;re per kWh, equivalent to .013 Euros or .017 US dollars per kWh. The<span>&#160;</span><b>CO<font size="11.2px"><sub style="line-height: 1; font-size: 11.2px">2</sub></font></b><span>&#160;</span>tax applies to all energy users, including the industrial sector. But the industrial companies can be taxed differently according to two principles: the process the energy is used for, and whether or not the company has entered into a voluntary agreement to apply energy efficiency measures. Danish policies like this provide incentives for companies to put in place more sustainable practices similar to a<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cap_and_trade" class="mw-redirect" title="Cap and trade" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">cap and trade</font></a><span>&#160;</span>program on carbon dioxide.<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-96" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-96" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[96]</a></sup></font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node ID="ID_297379433" CREATED="1553798487074" MODIFIED="1553798487074" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tax_refund"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
      In 1992, Denmark issued a carbon dioxide tax, which was about $14 for business and $7 for households, per ton of<span>&#160;</span><b>CO<font size="11.2px"><sub style="line-height: 1; font-size: 11.2px">2</sub></font></b>. However, Denmark offers a<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tax_refund" title="Tax refund" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">tax refund</font></a><span>&#160;</span>for energy efficient changes. One of the main goals for the tax is to have people change their habits, because most of the money collected would be put into research for alternative energy resources.<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-Morris,1994_97-0" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-Morris,1994-97" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[97]</a></sup></font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1577040398" CREATED="1553798487076" MODIFIED="1553798487076" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Carbon_tax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=26"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
