<node ID="ID_998436697" CREATED="1553798487242" MODIFIED="1553798487242" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Canadian_federal_election,_2008"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
      In the<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Canadian_federal_election,_2008" class="mw-redirect" title="Canadian federal election, 2008" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">2008 Canadian federal election</font></a>, a carbon tax proposed by<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liberal_Party_of_Canada" title="Liberal Party of Canada" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">Liberal Party</font></a><span>&#160;</span>leader<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/St%C3%A9phane_Dion" title="St&#xe9;phane Dion" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">St&#233;phane Dion</font></a>, known as the Green Shift, became a central issue in the campaign. It would have been revenue-neutral, with increased taxation on carbon being balanced by tax cuts for individual citizens. However, it proved to be unpopular and contributed to the defeat of Liberal Party with its worst share of the popular vote since<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Canadian_federal_election,_1867" class="mw-redirect" title="Canadian federal election, 1867" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">Confederation</font></a>.<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-167" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-167" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[167]</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-168" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-168" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[168]</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-169" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-169" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[169]</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-170" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-170" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[170]</a></sup></font><span>&#160;</span>By contrast, the Conservative party, who won the election, had promised to &quot;develop and implement a North American-wide<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cap-and-trade" class="mw-redirect" title="Cap-and-trade" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">cap-and-trade</font></a><span>&#160;</span>system for greenhouse gases and air pollution, with implementation to occur between 2012 and 2015.&quot;<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-171" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-171" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[171]</a></sup></font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node ID="ID_882399723" CREATED="1553798487246" MODIFIED="1553798487246" LINK="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_price_(Canada)"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
      In 2018, Canada passed the Greenhouse Gas Pollution Pricing Act implementing revenue-neutral<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_price_(Canada)" title="Carbon price (Canada)" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">carbon tax</font></a><span>&#160;</span>starting in 2019.<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-172" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-172" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[172]</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-Nuccitelli_173-0" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-Nuccitelli-173" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[173]</a></sup></font><span>&#160;</span>This fulfils a campaign pledge that<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Justin_Trudeau" title="Justin Trudeau" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">Justin Trudeau</font></a>made in 2015, before being elected as<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Canada" title="Prime Minister of Canada" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">Prime Minister of Canada</font></a>.<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-Nuccitelli_173-1" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-Nuccitelli-173" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[173]</a></sup></font><span>&#160;</span>The Greenhouse Gas Pollution Pricing Act will apply only to<span>&#160;</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Provinces_and_territories_of_Canada" title="Provinces and territories of Canada" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">provinces</font></a><span>&#160;</span>which do not have provincial carbon pricing systems meeting the federal requirements.<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-Nuccitelli_173-2" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-Nuccitelli-173" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[173]</a></sup></font><span>&#160;</span>In each province, the taxed money will be redistributed to citizens (<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Household" title="Household" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">households</font></a>).<font size="11.2px" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><sup id="cite_ref-Nuccitelli_173-3" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 11.2px"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax#cite_note-Nuccitelli-173" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">[173]</a></sup></font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
