      <span class="mw-headline" id="Harmonized_carbon_taxes">Harmonized carbon taxes</span><span class="mw-editsection-bracket" style="margin-right: 0; color: rgb(84, 89, 93)"><font color="rgb(84, 89, 93)" size="small" face="sans-serif">[</font></span><span class="mw-editsection" style="font-size: small; font-weight: normal; margin-left: 0; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; font-family: sans-serif; white-space: nowrap"><font size="small" face="sans-serif" color="rgb(11, 0, 128)"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Carbon_tax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=43" title="Edit section: Harmonized carbon taxes" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null">edit</a></font></span><span class="mw-editsection-bracket" style="margin-left: 0; color: rgb(84, 89, 93)"><font color="rgb(84, 89, 93)" size="small" face="sans-serif">]</font></span>
